{"content": "I'll solve this step-by-step using the conversion method.\n\n**Step 1: Convert inputs to base 10**\n\n884\u2089 to base 10:\n- 884\u2089 = 8\u00d79\u00b2 + 8\u00d79\u00b9 + 4\u00d79\u2070\n- = 8\u00d781 + 8\u00d79 + 4\u00d71\n- = 648 + 72 + 4\n- = 724\u2081\u2080\n\n846\u2089 to base 10:\n- 846\u2089 = 8\u00d79\u00b2 + 4\u00d79\u00b9 + 6\u00d79\u2070\n- = 8\u00d781 + 4\u00d79 + 6\u00d71\n- = 648 + 36 + 6\n- = 690\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n724\u2081\u2080 \u00d7 690\u2081\u2080 = 499,560\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result back to base 9**\n499,560 \u00f7 9 = 55,506 R 6 \u2192 Check: 55,506 \u00d7 9 + 6 = 499,560 \u2713\n55,506 \u00f7 9 = 6,167 R 3 \u2192 Check: 6,167 \u00d7 9 + 3 = 55,506 \u2713\n6,167 \u00f7 9 = 685 R 2 \u2192 Check: 685 \u00d7 9 + 2 = 6,167 \u2713\n685 \u00f7 9 = 76 R 1 \u2192 Check: 76 \u00d7 9 + 1 = 685 \u2713\n76 \u00f7 9 = 8 R 4 \u2192 Check: 8 \u00d7 9 + 4 = 76 \u2713\n8 \u00f7 9 = 0 R 8 \u2192 Check: 0 \u00d7 9 + 8 = 8 \u2713\n\nReading remainders from bottom to top: 841,236\u2089\n\n**Step 4: Verify**\n841,236\u2089 = 8\u00d79\u2075 + 4\u00d79\u2074 + 1\u00d79\u00b3 + 2\u00d79\u00b2 + 3\u00d79\u00b9 + 6\u00d79\u2070\n= 8\u00d759,049 + 4\u00d76,561 + 1\u00d7729 + 2\u00d781 + 3\u00d79 + 6\n= 472,392 + 26,244 + 729 + 162 + 27 + 6\n= 499,560\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n841236", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1134, "completion_tokens": 656}